---
import Spacer from './Spacer.astro';
import Button from './Button.astro';
import { Img } from 'astro-imagetools/components';
---
<div class="container">
    <div class="item">
        <div class="item-image">
            <Img src="/images/feature-01.jpg" format="webp" alt=""/>
        </div>
        <div class="item-textcontent inview-target">
            <div class="item-number rellax" data-rellax-speed="-0.6" data-rellax-percentage="4"><img src="/images/feature-number-01.svg" alt="01" width="250" height="200"></div>
            <div class="item-title">
                <div class="item-title-decoration"></div>
                一人当たりの受講生に対応できる時間がとても多い
            </div>
            <div class="item-body-text">
                <p>STUDIOつくばのSA（サポートアシスタント）って、まるでWEBの魔法使いみたいなんですよ！トレーナーの助っ人で、受講生の質問に超ウルトラフレンドリーに答えて、難しい壁をポイッと吹き飛ばしてくれます。トレーナーとSAの二人体制のおかげで、一人当たりの受講生に対応できる時間がとっても長いんです！みんなのことをサポートしてアシストしてアシスタントします！</p>
            </div>
            <Spacer height="40px" />
            <div class="item-button">
                <Button href="" label="詳しく見る" color="white" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<style>
    .container {
        position: relative;
    }
    .item {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        width: var(--content-width);
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .item-image {
        position: relative;
        width: 65%;
        margin: 0 0 0 -10%;
    }
    .item-textcontent {
        position: relative;
        width: 40%;
    }
    .item-title {
        font-size: 36px;
        margin: 0 0 32px;
    }
    .item-title-decoration {
        position: absolute;
        top: -48px;
        left: -48px;
        width: 64px;
        height: 64px;
        z-index: 2;
    }
    .item-title-decoration::before,
    .item-title-decoration::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: radial-gradient(at top center,#F8B7CB,#FF9191);
        box-shadow: var(--inner-grow-primary-small);
        opacity: 0;
    }
    .item-title-decoration::before {
        top: 4px;
        left: 28px;
        width: 32px;
        height: 32px;
    }
    .item-title-decoration::after {
        top: 36px;
        left: 4px;
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        filter: blur(2px);
    }
    .item-number {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        right: -40px;
        z-index: -1;
        width: 250px;
        transform: translate(0,-100%);
    }
    .item-body-text {
        line-height: 2;
    }
    .pagination {
        position: absolute;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 16px;
    }
    .pagination-bullet {
        width: 12px;
        height: 12px;
        background: var(--color-lightgray-primary);
        border-radius: 1000px;
        transition: transform 0.25s,background-color 0.25s;
    }
    .pagination-bullet.is-active {
        background: var(--color-orange-primary);
        transform: scale(1.2);
    }
    :where(.item-textcontent.is-inview) .item-title-decoration::before,
    :where(.item-textcontent.is-inview) .item-title-decoration::after {
        animation: inview-title-decoration-show 0.75s 0s normal both 1 ease-in-out;
    }
    :where(.item-textcontent.is-inview) .item-title-decoration::after {
        animation-delay: 0.125s;
    }
    .item-title,
    .item-body-text,
    .item-button {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translate(0,8px);
        transition: opacity 0.75s,transform 0.75s;
    }
    .item-title {
        transition-delay: 0s;
    }
    .item-body-text {
        transition-delay: 0.125s;
    }
    .item-button {
        transition-delay: 0.25s;
    }
    :where(.item-textcontent.is-inview) .item-title,
    :where(.item-textcontent.is-inview) .item-body-text,
    :where(.item-textcontent.is-inview) .item-button {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: none;
    }
    @keyframes inview-title-decoration-show {
        0% {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0);
        }
        50% {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        100% {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: scale(1);
        }
    }
</style>